      "section_index": 0,
      "section_kind": "weather_opening",
      "segments": [
        "s0"
      ],
      "start": 9.87,
      "text": "It is currently 17 degrees and cloudy in Berlin-Tempelhof."
    },
    {
      "end": 17.49,
      "id": "p1",
      "index": 1,
      "section_index": 1,
      "section_kind": "news_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s1"
      ],
      "start": 14.67,
      "text": "With the morning weather set, here is the news."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a5c7c9d6974",
        "a5026fa093c",
        "aa3c8a35747"
      ],
      "end": 53.74,
      "id": "p2",
      "index": 2,
      "section_index": 2,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3",
        "s4",
        "s5"
      ],
      "start": 17.95,
      "text": "The push for autonomous AI is moving from software into physical and recursive systems. Anthropic has released signals regarding AI that can build itself, while 1X Technologies launched a World Model Lab to scale intelligence for humanoid robots. Supporting this shift, NVIDIA has simplified the security of AI clusters by introducing intent-based profiles for Quantum InfiniBand. These updates allow network administrators to configure multi-tenant fabric security in minutes rather than days."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a68e293bb91",
        "a5d490a9a45"
      ],
      "end": 81.1,
      "id": "p3",
      "index": 3,
      "section_index": 3,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s6",
        "s7",
        "s8",
        "s9"
      ],
      "start": 54.02,
      "text": "This drive toward integration extends to both the desktop and orbital infrastructure. Moonshot AI has introduced Kimi Work, a desktop agent designed to move Chinese AI from simple chat interfaces into integrated productivity tools for knowledge workers. In Europe, the focus is on defense and space. Helsing and OHB have formed a joint venture to bridge the gap between AI startups and the broader European space sector."
    },
    {
      "end": 83.72,
      "id": "p4",
      "index": 4,
      "section_index": 4,
      "section_kind": "weather_return_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s10"
      ],
      "start": 81.24,
      "text": "After the headlines, back to the weather."
    },
    {
      "end": 84.42,
      "id": "p5",
      "index": 5,
      "section_index": 5,
      "section_kind": "weather_closing",
      "segments": [
        "s11"
      ],
      "start": 83.88,
      "text": "This afternoon will be cloudy with temperatures between 15 and 17 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 91.92,
      "id": "p6",
      "index": 6,
      "section_index": 6,
      "section_kind": "closing",
      "segments": [
        "s12"
      ],
      "start": 89.72,
      "text": "And that's it for your personal morning broadcast."
    },
    {
      "end": 97.64,
      "id": "p7",
      "index": 7,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s13"
      ],
      "start": 95.26,
      "text": "[mature adult voice, intensely emotional, tender, radiant; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    },
    {
      "end": 98.14,
      "id": "p8",
      "index": 8,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s14"
      ],
      "start": 97.64,
      "text": "[very very long pause before speaking; then mature adult voice, most emotional, strong, warm, radiant, deeply encouraging; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    }
  ],
